---
title: Peking Tofu Poke Bowl with Garlic Rice & Soy Mayo
description: We love poke bowls, because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This veggie version uses Peking-style tofu, Asian greens, carrot and cucumber, with a soy mayo to tie the whole thing together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5eb39f050e59d825c234958f-cdc5030c.jpg
